name: Red Rose Trap
description:
Sub-title: “Lovecraftian Floral Horror 001”

My inaugural, floral, cosmic horror nightmare. Red roses cross-bred with Venus flytraps and some unknowable genetic code passed down from The Old Ones create a hideous abomination of vegetation and eyes and micro-tentacles and disturbing orifices that could be used for consumption or excretion (or both).

Two artificial intelligence systems (VQGAN+CLIP) created this work. No input image was used.

2752x2752 pixel PNG

Minted December 11th, 2021. Verify via Twitter account @tormential and/or Instagram account @_tormential_ and/or vqgan.tormential.tez
